address: 51 Kensington Church Street, London W8 4BA, United Kingdom
author: Noor N.
description:
Really friendly staff, and a very warm and welcoming atmosphere.  And fresh bouquets on tables make this place even more lovely. 

Had the eggs Benedict special with beetroot hummus and a side of small french toast with fruits. Delicious food, great people. 

Will definitely come back for supper, there are some menu items I still want to try.
